universum.studios.android.fragment.manage

Annotation Type FragmentRequest.Transaction


  • @Retention(value=SOURCE)
public static @interface FragmentRequest.Transaction
    Defines an annotation for determining available transaction types for FragmentRequest.transaction(int) method.

    Available types:

    • FragmentRequest.REPLACE
    • FragmentRequest.ADD
    • FragmentRequest.REMOVE
    • FragmentRequest.SHOW
    • FragmentRequest.HIDE
    • FragmentRequest.ATTACH
    • FragmentRequest.DETACH
    See Also:
    FragmentRequest.transaction(int)
